140
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:57,441
(BELL RINGS)

141
00:06:01,195 --> 00:06:01,778
(WHACK)

142
00:06:04,489 --> 00:06:05,240
SERIOUSLY, MAN.

143
00:06:05,324 --> 00:06:07,576
I AM DONE
WITH THIS WHEELCHAIR.

144
00:06:07,659 --> 00:06:09,286
