YEAH. AND I WANT
MY LEFT NUT BACK,

145
00:06:09,369 --> 00:06:11,371
BUT WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO?

146
00:06:12,873 --> 00:06:14,041
(HEAVY EXHALE)

147
00:06:14,124 --> 00:06:16,502
(COMPUTER KEYS CLACK)

148
00:06:16,585 --> 00:06:18,045
SPINNER:
STEM CELLS?

149
00:06:18,128 --> 00:06:19,213
DON'T THOSE COME FROM
DEAD BABIES

150
00:06:19,296 --> 00:06:20,547
OR SOMETHING?

151
00:06:20,631 --> 00:06:22,257
NO, IDIOT.
THERE'S OTHER WAYS,

152
00:06:22,341 --> 00:06:24,218
LIKE UMBILICAL CORDS.

153
00:06:24,301 --> 00:06:25,302
