172
00:07:18,689 --> 00:07:19,857
YOU TOO.

173
00:07:22,401 --> 00:07:24,570
SO, HOW'S THE NEW RAMP?

174
00:07:24,653 --> 00:07:26,613
AHHH...
GETS THE JOB DONE.

175
00:07:26,697 --> 00:07:27,447
MR. BROOKS:
GREAT.

176
00:07:27,531 --> 00:07:29,700
LET ME FIND THAT INTERNSHIP
APPLICATION FOR YOU.

177
00:07:29,783 --> 00:07:31,118
ALL RIGHT.

178
00:07:33,829 --> 00:07:36,456
