THAT CAN WALK AGAIN.

195
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:13,660
MAYBE HE'S LUCKY.

196
00:08:13,744 --> 00:08:14,745
BUT...

197
00:08:16,413 --> 00:08:17,497
