198
00:08:17,581 --> 00:08:18,999
EVEN IF IT'S
ONE IN A MILLION -

199
00:08:19,082 --> 00:08:20,209
AND WE CAN AFFORD
THE TREATMENT -

200
00:08:20,292 --> 00:08:21,460
